50|$|However, the fuller {{meaning of}} tanzih is 'declaring incomparability', i.e. affirming <b>Allah's</b> transcendent {{distance}} from humanity. This concept is eternally juxtaposed with <b>Allah's</b> tashbih (closeness, or 'affirming similarity').|$|R
